Test organization patterns
Pattern	When to use
test.describe("group")	Group related tests for the same feature
test.beforeEach	Setup that runs before every test (e.g., navigate to page)
test.afterEach	Cleanup after every test
test.skip("reason")	Temporarily skip a test (better than commenting out)
test.only("name")	Run ONLY this test (for debugging — remove before committing!)